ADl.doc:
"stuff", "map_reduce", or "refine":

Stuff - Inputs all data into one prompt, limited by context length and unsuitable for larger documents.

Map_reduce - Processes data chunks and combines outputs, scalable for large documents but may lose information.

Refine - Iteratively processes documents, retains context, but more language model calls and no parallelization.
